{
  "video_id": "U5-yBjKKicA",
  "title": "What makes life worth living in the face of death | Lucy Kalanithi",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12780.0,
      "end_time": 19156.0,
      "text": "A few days after my husband Paul was diagnosed with stage IV lung cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19180.0,
      "end_time": 21676.0,
      "text": "we were lying in our bed at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21700.0,
      "end_time": 23476.0,
      "text": "and Paul said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23500.0,
      "end_time": 24700.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s going to be OK.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25860.0,
      "end_time": 28355.0,
      "text": "And I remember answering back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28380.0,
      "end_time": 29596.0,
      "text": "\"Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29620.0,
      "end_time": 33380.0,
      "text": "We just don&#39;t know what OK means yet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35140.0,
      "end_time": 38636.0,
      "text": "Paul and I had met as first-year medical students at Yale."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38660.0,
      "end_time": 42990.0,
      "text": "He was smart and kind and super funny."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42700.0,
      "end_time": 46516.0,
      "text": "He used to keep a gorilla suit in the trunk of his car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46540.0,
      "end_time": 48955.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;d say, \"It&#39;s for emergencies only.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48980.0,
      "end_time": 50180.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51200.0,
      "end_time": 54740.0,
      "text": "I fell in love with Paul as I watched the care he took with his patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55220.0,
      "end_time": 57396.0,
      "text": "He stayed late talking with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57420.0,
      "end_time": 60876.0,
      "text": "seeking to understand the experience of illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60900.0,
      "end_time": 63190.0,
      "text": "and not just its technicalities."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64379.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66595.0,
      "text": "He later told me he fell in love with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66620.0,
      "end_time": 71660.0,
      "text": "when he saw me cry over an EKG of a heart that had ceased beating."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72940.0,
      "end_time": 74476.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t know it yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74500.0,
      "end_time": 77636.0,
      "text": "but even in the heady days of young love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77660.0,
      "end_time": 80780.0,
      "text": "we were learning how to approach suffering together."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82660.0,
      "end_time": 85360.0,
      "text": "We got married and became doctors."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85600.0,
      "end_time": 87760.0,
      "text": "I was working as an internist"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87100.0,
      "end_time": 91155.0,
      "text": "and Paul was finishing his training as a neurosurgeon"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91180.0,
      "end_time": 92820.0,
      "text": "when he started to lose weight."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94300.0,
      "end_time": 99220.0,
      "text": "He developed excruciating back pain and a cough that wouldn&#39;t go away."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100220.0,
      "end_time": 102356.0,
      "text": "And when he was admitted to the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102380.0,
      "end_time": 106460.0,
      "text": "a CT scan revealed tumors in Paul&#39;s lungs and in his bones."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 108460.0,
      "end_time": 112590.0,
      "text": "We had both cared for patients with devastating diagnoses;"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 113200.0,
      "end_time": 115380.0,
      "text": "now it was our turn."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 118540.0,
      "end_time": 121140.0,
      "text": "We lived with Paul&#39;s illness for 22 months."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 121740.0,
      "end_time": 124259.0,
      "text": "He wrote a memoir about facing mortality."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 125140.0,
      "end_time": 127300.0,
      "text": "I gave birth to our daughter Cady,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 128600.0,
      "end_time": 129740.0,
      "text": "and we loved her and each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 130538.99999999999,
      "end_time": 135179.0,
      "text": "We learned directly how to struggle through really tough medical decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 137140.0,
      "end_time": 140714.0,
      "text": "The day we took Paul into the hospital for the last time"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 140739.0,
      "end_time": 142780.0,
      "text": "was the most difficult day of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 144380.0,
      "end_time": 146356.0,
      "text": "When he turned to me at the end"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 146380.0,
      "end_time": 148859.0,
      "text": "and said, \"I&#39;m ready,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 150820.0,
      "end_time": 153500.0,
      "text": "I knew that wasn&#39;t just a brave decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 154100.0,
      "end_time": 155420.0,
      "text": "It was the right one."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 156500.0,
      "end_time": 159380.0,
      "text": "Paul didn&#39;t want a ventilator and CPR."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 160180.0,
      "end_time": 161676.0,
      "text": "In that moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 161700.0,
      "end_time": 164299.0,
      "text": "the most important thing to Paul"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 165380.0,
      "end_time": 167600.0,
      "text": "was to hold our baby daughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 169600.0,
      "end_time": 170876.0,
      "text": "Nine hours later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 170900.0,
      "end_time": 172100.0,
      "text": "Paul died."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 175780.0,
      "end_time": 178360.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve always thought of myself as a caregiver --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 178600.0,
      "end_time": 180116.0,
      "text": "most physicians do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 180140.0,
      "end_time": 182940.0,
      "text": "and taking care of Paul deepened what that meant."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 183940.0,
      "end_time": 187556.0,
      "text": "Watching him reshape his identity during his illness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 187580.0,
      "end_time": 191760.0,
      "text": "learning to witness and accept his pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 191100.0,
      "end_time": 193636.0,
      "text": "talking together through his choices --"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 193660.0,
      "end_time": 195760.0,
      "text": "those experiences taught me"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 195100.0,
      "end_time": 200356.0,
      "text": "that resilience does not mean bouncing back to where you were before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 200380.0,
      "end_time": 203600.0,
      "text": "or pretending that the hard stuff isn&#39;t hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 203940.0,
      "end_time": 205940.0,
      "text": "It is so hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 206980.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s painful, messy stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 211140.0,
      "end_time": 212555.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s the stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 212580.0,
      "end_time": 215820.0,
      "text": "And I learned that when we approach it together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 216940.0,
      "end_time": 220620.0,
      "text": "we get to decide what success looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 222900.0,
      "end_time": 226220.0,
      "text": "One of the first things Paul said to me after his diagnosis was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 227180.0,
      "end_time": 228700.0,
      "text": "\"I want you to get remarried.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 230300.0,
      "end_time": 233636.0,
      "text": "And I was like, whoa, I guess we get to say anything out loud."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 233660.0,
      "end_time": 236196.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 236220.0,
      "end_time": 238276.0,
      "text": "It was so shocking"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 238300.0,
      "end_time": 240100.0,
      "text": "and heartbreaking ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 242476.0,
      "text": "and generous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 242500.0,
      "end_time": 243996.0,
      "text": "and really comforting"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244200.0,
      "end_time": 246596.0,
      "text": "because it was so starkly honest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 246620.0,
      "end_time": 249740.0,
      "text": "and that honesty turned out to be exactly what we needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 250580.0,
      "end_time": 252276.0,
      "text": "Early in Paul&#39;s illness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 252300.0,
      "end_time": 255660.0,
      "text": "we agreed we would just keep saying things out loud."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 257220.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259516.00000000003,
      "text": "Tasks like making a will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 259540.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262196.0,
      "text": "or completing our advance directives --"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 262220.0,
      "end_time": 264796.0,
      "text": "tasks that I had always avoided --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 264820.0,
      "end_time": 267990.0,
      "text": "were not as daunting as they once seemed."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 267860.0,
      "end_time": 272219.0,
      "text": "I realized that completing an advance directive is an act of love --"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 273300.0,
      "end_time": 274860.0,
      "text": "like a wedding vow."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 275540.0,
      "end_time": 277796.0,
      "text": "A pact to take care of someone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 277820.0,
      "end_time": 280116.0,
      "text": "codifying the promise"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 280140.0,
      "end_time": 282600.0,
      "text": "that til death do us part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 283600.0,
      "end_time": 284300.0,
      "text": "I will be there."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 285780.0,
      "end_time": 288219.0,
      "text": "If needed, I will speak for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 289200.0,
      "end_time": 291299.0,
      "text": "I will honor your wishes."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 293100.0,
      "end_time": 296460.0,
      "text": "That paperwork became a tangible part of our love story."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 298860.0,
      "end_time": 300760.0,
      "text": "As physicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 300100.0,
      "end_time": 301756.0,
      "text": "Paul and I were in a good position"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 301780.0,
      "end_time": 304940.0,
      "text": "to understand and even accept his diagnosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 305940.0,
      "end_time": 307276.0,
      "text": "We weren&#39;t angry about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 307300.0,
      "end_time": 308516.0,
      "text": "luckily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 308540.0,
      "end_time": 312676.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;d seen so many patients in devastating situations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 312700.0,
      "end_time": 315380.0,
      "text": "and we knew that death is a part of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 317700.0,
      "end_time": 319276.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s one thing to know that;"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 319300.0,
      "end_time": 320956.0,
      "text": "it was a very different experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 320980.0,
      "end_time": 325460.0,
      "text": "to actually live with the sadness and uncertainty of a serious illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 326540.0,
      "end_time": 329756.0,
      "text": "Huge strides are being made against lung cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 329780.0,
      "end_time": 334539.0,
      "text": "but we knew that Paul likely had months to a few years left to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 336540.0,
      "end_time": 337756.0,
      "text": "During that time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 337780.0,
      "end_time": 340580.0,
      "text": "Paul wrote about his transition from doctor to patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 341500.0,
      "end_time": 345556.0,
      "text": "He talked about feeling like he was suddenly at a crossroads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 345580.0,
      "end_time": 348380.0,
      "text": "and how he would have thought he&#39;d be able to see the path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 349140.0,
      "end_time": 351876.0,
      "text": "that because he treated so many patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 351900.0,
      "end_time": 354179.0,
      "text": "maybe he could follow in their footsteps."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 355100.0,
      "end_time": 356900.0,
      "text": "But he was totally disoriented."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 360360.0,
      "text": "Rather than a path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 360600.0,
      "end_time": 361556.0,
      "text": "Paul wrote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 361580.0,
      "end_time": 363635.0,
      "text": "\"I saw instead"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 363660.0,
      "end_time": 367820.0,
      "text": "only a harsh, vacant, gleaming white desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 368540.0,
      "end_time": 371700.0,
      "text": "As if a sandstorm had erased all familiarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 372980.0,
      "end_time": 374820.0,
      "text": "I had to face my mortality"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 375820.0,
      "end_time": 379420.0,
      "text": "and try to understand what made my life worth living,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 380500.0,
      "end_time": 383980.0,
      "text": "and I needed my oncologist&#39;s help to do so.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 389316.0,
      "text": "The clinicians taking care of Paul"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 389340.0,
      "end_time": 393556.0,
      "text": "gave me an even deeper appreciation for my colleagues in health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 393580.0,
      "end_time": 395556.0,
      "text": "We have a tough job."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 395580.0,
      "end_time": 400356.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re responsible for helping patients have clarity around their prognoses"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 400380.0,
      "end_time": 402356.0,
      "text": "and their treatment options,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 402380.0,
      "end_time": 404876.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s never easy, but it&#39;s especially tough"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 404900.0,
      "end_time": 408580.0,
      "text": "when you&#39;re dealing with potentially terminal illnesses like cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 410140.0,
      "end_time": 413836.0,
      "text": "Some people don&#39;t want to know how long they have left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 413860.0,
      "end_time": 415600.0,
      "text": "others do."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 415660.0,
      "end_time": 418140.0,
      "text": "Either way, we never have those answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 420200.0,
      "end_time": 422859.0,
      "text": "Sometimes we substitute hope"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 423900.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "by emphasizing the best-case scenario."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 428140.0,
      "end_time": 430236.0,
      "text": "In a survey of physicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 430260.0,
      "end_time": 435750.0,
      "text": "55 percent said they painted a rosier picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 435100.0,
      "end_time": 436556.0,
      "text": "than their honest opinion"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 436580.0,
      "end_time": 438539.0,
      "text": "when describing a patient&#39;s prognosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 439780.0,
      "end_time": 442500.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an instinct born out of kindness."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 443940.0,
      "end_time": 445356.0,
      "text": "But researchers have found"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 445380.0,
      "end_time": 450596.0,
      "text": "that when people better understand the possible outcomes of an illness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 450620.0,
      "end_time": 452140.0,
      "text": "they have less anxiety,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 452900.0,
      "end_time": 454659.0,
      "text": "greater ability to plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 455660.0,
      "end_time": 457980.0,
      "text": "and less trauma for their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 460620.0,
      "end_time": 463356.0,
      "text": "Families can struggle with those conversations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 463380.0,
      "end_time": 469860.0,
      "text": "but for us, we also found that information immensely helpful with big decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 470740.0,
      "end_time": 471940.0,
      "text": "Most notably,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 472860.0,
      "end_time": 474600.0,
      "text": "whether to have a baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 476620.0,
      "end_time": 481580.0,
      "text": "Months to a few years meant Paul was not likely to see her grow up."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 482660.0,
      "end_time": 485156.0,
      "text": "But he had a good chance of being there for her birth"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 485180.0,
      "end_time": 486820.0,
      "text": "and for the beginning of her life."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 488460.0,
      "end_time": 490436.0,
      "text": "I remember asking Paul"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 490460.0,
      "end_time": 493835.0,
      "text": "if he thought having to say goodbye to a child"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 493860.0,
      "end_time": 496380.0,
      "text": "would make dying even more painful."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 498220.0,
      "end_time": 500760.0,
      "text": "And his answer astounded me."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 500100.0,
      "end_time": 501796.0,
      "text": "He said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 501820.0,
      "end_time": 504600.0,
      "text": "\"Wouldn&#39;t it be great if it did?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 507860.0,
      "end_time": 509600.0,
      "text": "And we did it."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 509660.0,
      "end_time": 512220.0,
      "text": "Not in order to spite cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 513340.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515196.00000000006,
      "text": "but because we were learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 515220.0,
      "end_time": 520380.0,
      "text": "that living fully means accepting suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 523700.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526116.0,
      "text": "Paul&#39;s oncologist tailored his chemo"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 526140.0,
      "end_time": 529436.0,
      "text": "so he could continue working as a neurosurgeon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 529460.0,
      "end_time": 531900.0,
      "text": "which initially we thought was totally impossible."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 533340.0,
      "end_time": 534636.0,
      "text": "When the cancer advanced"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 534660.0,
      "end_time": 537180.0,
      "text": "and Paul shifted from surgery to writing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 538200.0,
      "end_time": 541356.0,
      "text": "his palliative care doctor prescribed a stimulant medication"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 541380.0,
      "end_time": 542980.0,
      "text": "so he could be more focused."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 544420.0,
      "end_time": 548990.0,
      "text": "They asked Paul about his priorities and his worries."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 548900.0,
      "end_time": 552540.0,
      "text": "They asked him what trade-offs he was willing to make."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 554300.0,
      "end_time": 558435.0,
      "text": "Those conversations are the best way to ensure"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 558460.0,
      "end_time": 562340.0,
      "text": "that your health care matches your values."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 564100.0,
      "end_time": 566756.0,
      "text": "Paul joked that it&#39;s not like that \"birds and bees\" talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 566780.0,
      "end_time": 568116.0,
      "text": "you have with your parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 568140.0,
      "end_time": 570675.0,
      "text": "where you all get it over with as quickly as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 570700.0,
      "end_time": 572396.0,
      "text": "and then pretend it never happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 572420.0,
      "end_time": 575315.0,
      "text": "You revisit the conversation as things change."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 575340.0,
      "end_time": 578260.0,
      "text": "You keep saying things out loud."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 580220.0,
      "end_time": 581476.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m forever grateful"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 581500.0,
      "end_time": 583876.0,
      "text": "because Paul&#39;s clinicians felt"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 583900.0,
      "end_time": 586996.0,
      "text": "that their job wasn&#39;t to try to give us answers they didn&#39;t have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 587200.0,
      "end_time": 590396.0,
      "text": "or only to try to fix things for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 590420.0,
      "end_time": 593219.0,
      "text": "but to counsel Paul through painful choices ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 594140.0,
      "end_time": 599140.0,
      "text": "when his body was failing but his will to live wasn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 601260.0,
      "end_time": 602819.0,
      "text": "Later, after Paul died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 603780.0,
      "end_time": 606476.0,
      "text": "I received a dozen bouquets of flowers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 606500.0,
      "end_time": 608200.0,
      "text": "but I sent just one ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 608900.0,
      "end_time": 610956.0,
      "text": "to Paul&#39;s oncologist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 610980.0,
      "end_time": 614436.0,
      "text": "because she supported his goals"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 614460.0,
      "end_time": 617200.0,
      "text": "and she helped him weigh his choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 618340.0,
      "end_time": 623200.0,
      "text": "She knew that living means more than just staying alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 625540.0,
      "end_time": 628435.0,
      "text": "A few weeks ago, a patient came into my clinic."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 628460.0,
      "end_time": 631620.0,
      "text": "A woman dealing with a serious chronic disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 632700.0,
      "end_time": 635596.0,
      "text": "And while we were talking about her life and her health care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 635620.0,
      "end_time": 639100.0,
      "text": "she said, \"I love my palliative care team."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 639980.0,
      "end_time": 642200.0,
      "text": "They taught me that it&#39;s OK to say &#39;no&#39;.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 643460.0,
      "end_time": 645260.0,
      "text": "Yeah, I thought, of course it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 646660.0,
      "end_time": 648900.0,
      "text": "But many patients don&#39;t feel that."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 650660.0,
      "end_time": 652795.0,
      "text": "Compassion and Choices did a study"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 652820.0,
      "end_time": 656200.0,
      "text": "where they asked people about their health care preferences."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 656580.0,
      "end_time": 660636.0,
      "text": "And a lot of people started their answers with the words"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 660660.0,
      "end_time": 662100.0,
      "text": "\"Well, if I had a choice ...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 663860.0,
      "end_time": 665420.0,
      "text": "If I had a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 666700.0,
      "end_time": 668596.0,
      "text": "And when I read that \"if,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 668620.0,
      "end_time": 670796.0,
      "text": "I understood better"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 670820.0,
      "end_time": 673676.0,
      "text": "why one in four people"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 673700.0,
      "end_time": 678556.0,
      "text": "receives excessive or unwanted medical treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 678580.0,
      "end_time": 683740.0,
      "text": "or watches a family member receive excessive or unwanted medical treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 685420.0,
      "end_time": 687516.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not because doctors don&#39;t get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 687540.0,
      "end_time": 688740.0,
      "text": "We do."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 689340.0,
      "end_time": 692276.0,
      "text": "We understand the real psychological consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 692300.0,
      "end_time": 694660.0,
      "text": "on patients and their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 695580.0,
      "end_time": 697420.0,
      "text": "The things is, we deal with them, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 698540.0,
      "end_time": 703876.0,
      "text": "Half of critical care nurses and a quarter of ICU doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 703900.0,
      "end_time": 706435.0,
      "text": "have considered quitting their jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 706460.0,
      "end_time": 711356.0,
      "text": "because of distress over feeling that for some of their patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 711380.0,
      "end_time": 714780.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve provided care that didn&#39;t fit with the person&#39;s values."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 717220.0,
      "end_time": 719716.0,
      "text": "But doctors can&#39;t make sure your wishes are respected"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 719740.0,
      "end_time": 721940.0,
      "text": "until they know what they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 723820.0,
      "end_time": 727540.0,
      "text": "Would you want to be on life support if it offered any chance of longer life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 728820.0,
      "end_time": 732436.0,
      "text": "Are you most worried about the quality of that time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 732460.0,
      "end_time": 733660.0,
      "text": "rather than quantity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 734540.0,
      "end_time": 737819.0,
      "text": "Both of those choices are thoughtful and brave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 739200.0,
      "end_time": 740860.0,
      "text": "but for all of us, it&#39;s our choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 742200.0,
      "end_time": 743740.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s true at the end of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 744740.0,
      "end_time": 747316.0,
      "text": "and for medical care throughout our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 747340.0,
      "end_time": 750196.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re pregnant, do you want genetic screening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 750220.0,
      "end_time": 752140.0,
      "text": "Is a knee replacement right or not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 753420.0,
      "end_time": 756740.0,
      "text": "Do you want to do dialysis in a clinic or at home?"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 758420.0,
      "end_time": 759620.0,
      "text": "The answer is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 760460.0,
      "end_time": 761660.0,
      "text": "it depends."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 762380.0,
      "end_time": 766860.0,
      "text": "What medical care will help you live the way you want to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 768900.0,
      "end_time": 771116.0,
      "text": "I hope you remember that question"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 771140.0,
      "end_time": 774300.0,
      "text": "the next time you face a decision in your health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 775200.0,
      "end_time": 778600.0,
      "text": "Remember that you always have a choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 779600.0,
      "end_time": 784780.0,
      "text": "and it is OK to say no to a treatment that&#39;s not right for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 786420.0,
      "end_time": 789795.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a poem by W.S. Merwin --"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 789820.0,
      "end_time": 792116.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s just two sentences long --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 792140.0,
      "end_time": 794260.0,
      "text": "that captures how I feel now."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 796820.0,
      "end_time": 799916.0,
      "text": "\"Your absence has gone through me"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 799940.0,
      "end_time": 802460.0,
      "text": "like thread through a needle."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 803620.0,
      "end_time": 807100.0,
      "text": "Everything I do is stitched with its color.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 809300.0,
      "end_time": 812579.0,
      "text": "For me that poem evokes my love for Paul,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 813340.0,
      "end_time": 815316.0,
      "text": "and a new fortitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 815340.0,
      "end_time": 818380.0,
      "text": "that came from loving and losing him."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 820180.0,
      "end_time": 822579.0,
      "text": "When Paul said, \"It&#39;s going to be OK,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 823820.0,
      "end_time": 827500.0,
      "text": "that didn&#39;t mean that we could cure his illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 828420.0,
      "end_time": 833939.0,
      "text": "Instead, we learned to accept both joy and sadness at the same time;"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 835600.0,
      "end_time": 838356.0,
      "text": "to uncover beauty and purpose"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 838380.0,
      "end_time": 842540.0,
      "text": "both despite and because we are all born"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 843340.0,
      "end_time": 844540.0,
      "text": "and we all die."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 846340.0,
      "end_time": 848900.0,
      "text": "And for all the sadness and sleepless nights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 849700.0,
      "end_time": 851140.0,
      "text": "it turns out there is joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 852260.0,
      "end_time": 854876.0,
      "text": "I leave flowers on Paul&#39;s grave"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 854900.0,
      "end_time": 857620.0,
      "text": "and watch our two-year-old run around on the grass."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 859600.0,
      "end_time": 863660.0,
      "text": "I build bonfires on the beach and watch the sunset with our friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 865340.0,
      "end_time": 869100.0,
      "text": "Exercise and mindfulness meditation have helped a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 870620.0,
      "end_time": 871916.0,
      "text": "And someday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 871940.0,
      "end_time": 873500.0,
      "text": "I hope I do get remarried."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 876380.0,
      "end_time": 879140.0,
      "text": "Most importantly, I get to watch our daughter grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 880540.0,
      "end_time": 884435.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve thought a lot about what I&#39;m going to say to her"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 884460.0,
      "end_time": 885700.0,
      "text": "when she&#39;s older."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 888220.0,
      "end_time": 889420.0,
      "text": "\"Cady,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 890580.0,
      "end_time": 893796.0,
      "text": "engaging in the full range of experience --"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 893820.0,
      "end_time": 895516.0,
      "text": "living and dying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 895540.0,
      "end_time": 897200.0,
      "text": "love and loss --"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 897860.0,
      "end_time": 899140.0,
      "text": "is what we get to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 900900.0,
      "end_time": 905939.0,
      "text": "Being human doesn&#39;t happen despite suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 907500.0,
      "end_time": 908780.0,
      "text": "It happens within it."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 910780.0,
      "end_time": 912500.0,
      "text": "When we approach suffering together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 913420.0,
      "end_time": 915500.0,
      "text": "when we choose not to hide from it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 916900.0,
      "end_time": 918316.0,
      "text": "our lives don&#39;t diminish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 918340.0,
      "end_time": 919540.0,
      "text": "they expand.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 921700.0,
      "end_time": 924420.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve learned that cancer isn&#39;t always a battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 926220.0,
      "end_time": 927876.0,
      "text": "Or if it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 927900.0,
      "end_time": 930900.0,
      "text": "maybe it&#39;s a fight for something different than we thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 932460.0,
      "end_time": 934820.0,
      "text": "Our job isn&#39;t to fight fate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 935980.0,
      "end_time": 937700.0,
      "text": "but to help each other through."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 939100.0,
      "end_time": 940620.0,
      "text": "Not as soldiers"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 941820.0,
      "end_time": 943200.0,
      "text": "but as shepherds."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 945740.0,
      "end_time": 947796.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how we make it OK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
